      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The Northern Pacific will continue\nthe Sunday excursions to st. Maries'\nFerrelrs and st. Joe during the sum\nmer. Train will leave Spokane a.\nm for Occur d'Alene. Steamer Cakes\nleaving there on arrival or train TOT\ndelightful ride across the lake and\nIN the st. Joe river. arriving at Fer\nrelrs about 2 p. m. where stop of\n40 minutes will be made for dinner.\nThose preferring to do so can take\nlunch baskets and eat lunch on the\nboat. Returning train will arrive\nSpokane about p m. Fare for the\nround trip 81.\n\n\nJ. W. HILL, Gen. Agt."
    }
  ]
